name: This is not a goodbye
description:
Dear, You.

Hey beautiful soul, thank you for being you. You are such a special person and there is a lot of magical things that I feel when I'm with you.

I’m still counting the days until you left me with sweet memories and thoughts of you.

I wish there is a way that I could see you again and again.
But people say that God hates us. 

They say God hates us because we choose to fall in love on our own.

“God hates the differences,” they said.

But don't worry, I still believe in us.

For me, they’re not telling the truth.

That's all.

Ps: This is not a goodbye. But a chance to say “see you later.” And I really mean it.

Regards - Yohn
